{"tid":778350,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有沒巴打轉工無耐就後悔","createTime":"2018-08-13T15:30:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T18:05:20.000Z","uid":22148,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"631f955073ac49c6c0cc392358c66916ff5534da","tid":778350,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:30:39.000Z","msg":"岩岩轉咗新工一個月左右<br />\n先發覺舊老闆好好 舊公司都唔錯<br />\n又有下屬幫手<br />\n同事又肯幫手<br />\n<br />\n而家人工係高咗少少<br />\n但乜都要落手落腳去做<br />\nD同事又唔helpful<br />\n而新老闆要求又好高<br />\n乜都唔講清講楚<br />\n但乜都要你做足120分<br />\n唉<br />\n返工返到好大壓力<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf85432e7ac0d62500fc0058336a7e0a330b411","tid":778350,"uid":55,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:47:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f18d3d2f2e63f2d7b73259c07da98da4c4786183","tid":778350,"uid":110112,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但已經冇得返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  每日都好後悔<br />\n而家呢份工唔係好差<br />\n但上一份好好多好多"},{"pid":"cdeadadffafbfaa30ce422f2206702d5ef2171c1","tid":778350,"uid":55233,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:49:55.000Z","msg":"same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n走咗之後先發覺舊公司其實算好好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d89db25916b2b00305d77597f393f8e520ee00","tid":778350,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"0bf85432e7ac0d62500fc0058336a7e0a330b411","tid":778350,"uid":55,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:47:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-